WEBVTT

00:01:58.187 --> 00:02:02.771
Ni nyenzo yenye nguvu ambayo
inahusisha uoni na maarifa

00:02:02.795 --> 00:02:07.278
na kutengeneza uelewa wetu wa
wapi tulipo na kipi tunachoona.

00:02:08.535 --> 00:02:11.576
Huu ni mfano wa kazi ya sanaa

00:02:11.600 --> 00:02:14.529
ambao umenikumbusha kwamba
maarifa ya uono --

00:02:14.553 --> 00:02:16.503
ni mchakato endelevu

00:02:16.527 --> 00:02:18.579
na ambao hauwezi fikiwa tamati kamwe.

00:02:19.121 --> 00:02:22.911
Nilikutana na hii sanaa ya kufikirika
ambayo ni tulivu,

00:02:22.935 --> 00:02:25.238
na ilibidi nisogee kwa ukaribu mara mbili,

00:02:25.262 --> 00:02:26.478
hata mara tatu,

00:02:26.502 --> 00:02:29.564
kuelewa kwanini inavuma kwa undani sana.